{"tid":847660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"88歲老翁元朗大馬路墮樓亡","createTime":"2018-10-04T10:32:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-04T10:57:08.000Z","uid":41404,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"93902eec8cb407bd3da28db415255d63dd6cd7cb","tid":847660,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T10:32:24.000Z","msg":"元朗青山公路196號對開，中午12時半左右，一名男子由高處墮下，倒卧地上。救援人員到場證實姓陳(88歲)男事主已告不治，警方封鎖現場調查，懷疑陳伯從上址天台墮下，警方在現場撿獲遺書，初步調查相信事件沒有可疑，死因有待驗屍確定。據悉，陳伯有身體病紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181004/58754726\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181004%2F58754726&d=z2mhxptcnXvYxAH54PNQzb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=839c32b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181004%2F58754726&h=19d72ce5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181004/58754726</a>"},{"pid":"cba5349930e6b26952afe940ecad4909e05a2ee2","tid":847660,"uid":50740,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T10:32:59.000Z","msg":"福氣"},{"pid":"c50b6b9b41537ffb96c5205eb3d546975e726297","tid":847660,"uid":42188,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T10:40:55.000Z","msg":"$2客-1"},{"pid":"09f90a62c064b996550ac8e6313681d636617d4a","tid":847660,"uid":94828,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T10:51:16.000Z","msg":"廢老少少辛苦都唔捱得"},{"pid":"316b3b83f522633385f4005b47812daa1ffd166e","tid":847660,"uid":146376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T10:57:08.000Z","msg":"跳還跳 因住壓親我d牛"}]}